ABOUT.HEAD: Akai na
ABOUT.P1: Ni mai son injina ne mai son software tare da tushe mai karfi a duka fronted da kuma kwarin gwiwa.
ABOUT.P2: A cikin 'yan shekarun nan, na mai da hankali kan atomatik, tsarin ciniki, da kuma dandamali AI-fitar da dandamali.
ABOUT.P3: Kamar yadda nayi ci gaba da tsaftace dabarun fasaha da nazarin nazarin, Ina nufin gado bagin tsakanin fasaha da kasuwanci.

WORK.HEAD: Gwanintan aiki
WORK.WD1: Ci gaba da hade da hutawa da sabulu apis, inganta lokutan amsa da kashi 20%.
WORK.WD2: Ingantaccen musayar mai amfani, haɓaka gamsuwa da 15%.
WORK.WD3: An gano da warware kwari masu mahimmanci a kan dit kuma suna zama matakai, inganta nasarar nasarar jigilar kayayyaki ya ragu da 25%.
WORK.WD4: Hadin gwiwar kungiyoyi masu aiki don tabbatar da zamani da kuma cikakkiyar isar da aikin ci gaba, inganta ayyukan tiyata gaba daya ta 10%.

DESC.AN: Telegroro bot don karɓar saƙonni marasa amfani, tare da tallafin yanar gizo don masu amfani da telegrag.
DESC.FL: Tsarin kasuwancin da sauri, yanayin kula da wutar lantarki wanda yake ƙarfafa sigina don ingantacciyar daidaito da atomatik.
DESC.GU: Amfani da tushen yanar gizo don kawo feetching, rarrabuwa, takaita da gudanar da labarai na duniya da labaran amfani da GDelt 2.0 api.
DESC.LG: Wani dandalin AIGI-mai sarrafa kansa-mai sarrafa kai na AIDI na ASHIGED DANGREGORD DON WANNAN LABARI.
DESC.PT: Wani mai tsauri da kuma ma'amala na aiki na aikina, dabarun, da ayyukan.
DESC.IM: Tsarin aikin sarrafa kayan windows-tushen da aka gina a cikin studio studio 2019. Yana fasalta abu rarrabe, kashe kudi, samar da mafi inganci har yanzu tasiri mai sauki don bin diddigin hannun jari da kudi.
DESC.WK: Ainihin-lokacin atomatik Charfin Haɗin kai tsaye don shafukan wasan caca don wasanni na wasanni.
